<p>I really think my version is less wrong.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1rgo"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1rgo" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1rgo')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1rgo" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1rgo')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1rgo" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1ud/rationality_quotes_march_2010/1rgo?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_1rgo" href="#1r4z" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1rgo" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1rgo')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1rgo class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1rgo" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1rgi" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1rgi" class="parent"><a name="1rgi" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1rgi" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1rgi" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1rgi" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/ata/">ata</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">16 March 2010 05:56:30AM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1rgi'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1rgi')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1rgi" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1rgi" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/ata/">ata</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">16 March 2010 05:56:30AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1rgi'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1rgi'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1rgi')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1rgi" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>There are postmodernist artists and authors whom I really do appreciate but most them are just people who think putting the word "society" into something they did without much thought would instantly make them an artist.</p>
