lick="return hidecomment('t1_1p45')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1p45" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>Science is the only news. When you scan through a newspaper or magazine, all the human interest stuff is the same old he-said-she-said, the politics and economics the same sorry cyclic dramas, the fashions a pathetic illusion of newness, and even the technology is predictable if you know the science. Human nature doesn’t change much; science does, and the change accrues, altering the world irreversibly.</p>
