xpand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1p0d')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1p0d" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>I haven't taken this position just to be difficult. To look around, the world does appear to be flat, so I think it is incumbent on others to prove decisively that it isn't. And I don't think that burden of proof has been met yet.</p>
