ment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1p56" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/JohannesDahlstrom/">JohannesDahlstrom</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 March 2010 11:41:50PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1p56'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1p56'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1p56')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1p56" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Oops. I do feel a bit embarrassed for just assuming that the strip in question was recent enough not to have been posted to last month's thread. Voted in favor of the proposed norm.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1p56"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1p56" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1p56')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1p56" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1p56')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1p56" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1ud/rationality_quotes_march_2010/1p56?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_1p56" href="#1p1g" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1p56" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1p56')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1p56 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1p56" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1p1v" class="morechildren" ><div id="pre_t1_1p1v" class="parent"></div><div id="entry_t1_1p1v" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1p1v" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'></div><div id="display_t1_1p1v" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"></div><div id="body_t1_1p1v" class="comment-content"><span class="morecomments"><a style="font-size: smaller; font-weight: bold" id="more_t1_1p1v" href="javascript:void()" onclick="return morechildren(this, 't3_1ud', ['1p1v'], 2)">load more comments<span class="gray">&nbsp;(9 replies)</span></a></span></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1p1v"></div><div class="comment-links"></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1p1v" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1p38" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1p38" class="parent"><a name="1p38" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1p38" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1p38" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1p38" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/saliency/">saliency</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 March 2010 09:44:22PM</span><span class="votes " >2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1p38'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1p38')">[+] (5 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1p38" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1p38" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/saliency/">saliency</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 March 2010 09:44:22PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1p38'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1p38'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1p38')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1p38" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Scrapheap Transhumanism:</p>

<p>"I’m sort of inured to pain by this point. Anesthetic is illegal for people like me, so we learn to live without it; I’ve made scalpel incisions in my hands, pushed five-millimeter diameter needles through my skin, and once used a vegetable knife to carve a cavity into the tip of my index finger. I’m an idiot, but I’m an idiot working in the name of progress: I’m Lepht Anonym, scrapheap transhumanist. I work with what I can get."</p>

<p>Here is more: 
<a href="http://hplusmagazine.com/articles/enhanced/scrapheap-transhumanism" rel="nofollow">http://hplusmagazine.com/articles/enhanced/scrapheap-transhumanism</a></p>

<p>HT:Tyler Cowen</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1p38"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1p38" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1p38')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1p38" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1p38')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1p38" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1ud/rationality_quotes_march_2010/1p38?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1p38" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1p38')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1p38 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1p38" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_1p38" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_1p38" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1pac" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1pac" class="parent"><a name="1pac" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1pac" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1pac" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1pac" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/AngryParsley/">AngryParsley</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 March 2010 07:35:31AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1pac'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1pac')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1pac" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1pac" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/AngryParsley/">AngryParsley</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 March 2010 07:35:31AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1pac'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1pac'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1pac')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1pac" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Interesting article, but that guy could have avoided some suffering if he knew about ways to lessen pain without anesthetic. A common technique used by body piercers is to numb the area with ice beforehand.</p>

<p>Really though, most of the benefits of those things don't require any cutting. Why not wear the RFID tag in a bracelet? Why not temporarily glue rare earth magnets to his fingertips? If that guy ever needs an MRI, he'll have to get the magnets removed from his body. If he's in an accident and the doctors don't know about his magnets, the MRI could injure him or damage the scanner.</p>

<p>Edit: Oh, <a href="http://sapiensanonym.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow">he has a blog</a>. It's umm... interesting.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1pac"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1pac" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1pac')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1pac" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1pac')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1pac" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1ud/rationality_quotes_march_2010/1pac?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_1pac" href="#1p38" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1pac" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1pac')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1pac class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1pac" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_1pac" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_1pac" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1y3j" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1y3j" class="parent"><a name="1y3j" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1y3j" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1y3j" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1y3j" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/gwern/">gwern</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 May 2010 12:47:14AM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1y3j'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1y3j')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1y3j" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1y3j" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/gwern/">gwern</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 May 2010 12:47:14AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1y3j'>0 points</span><script type="text/ja